collection_details.name: Winds of Yawanawa by Yawanawa and Refik Anadol
collection_details.description:
A first-of-its-kind space of co-creation between the Brazilian Indigenous Yawanawa community and media artist Refik Anadol.

Launching this historical collaboration, the Yawanawa community and Refik Anadol Studio have co-authored the Genesis collection 'Winds of Yawanawa'. The collection of 1000 unique Data Paintings brings the nuances of Yawanawa art to the digital world with the aim of preserving the community’s rich culture.

First and only official collaborative wallet of Refik Anadol, with Instituto Nixiwaka; representing the Yawanawa communities of Aldeia Sagrada and Nova Esperança.

collection_details.name: MATR1X KUKU

collection_details.name: HV-MTL
collection_details.description: The HV-MTL (Heavy Metal) collection is made up of 30,000 Mechs derived from 8 different Power Source types. Beginning March 15, 2023, eligible Sewer Passes can be burned to summon a Power Source that will reveal an Evo 1 Mech. Evo 1 holders can participate in future minigame sets with their Evo 1s to unlock additional HV-MTL evolution stages. Holders of HV-MTLs are subject to the HV-MTL License Agreement available at https://hv-mtl.com/hvmtl-license-agreement.

collection_details.name: InfiniGods - InfiniPass
collection_details.description:
The InfiniPass is an all-access pass to the InfiniGods Universe (IGU) of blockchain games. Passes provide access to early gameplay content, bonus play periods, exclusive NFT drops, powerful boosts, and much more — for life. 

Two passes exist in the IGU: the Community Pass and Ultimate Pass.

The Community Pass (3,188 exist): Designed for a broader group of gamers. Provides early access to InfiniGods games, special perks during future mints, passive gameplay boosts, and access to exclusive tournaments & prize pools.

The Ultimate Pass (260 exist): Designed for those that want to travel deeper into the InfiniGods Universe as a VIP. Provides all benefits of the Community Pass, plus: free NFTs for every InfiniGods release in perpetuity, enhanced gameplay boosts, access to the Roundtable (private VIP Discord community), & inside access to the IG game development team.

collection_details.name: Chonks
collection_details.description:
Chonks is a fully onchain PFP collection with collectable, composable Traits. 

Each Chonk has a token bound account (or its own wallet) that holds the individual Trait tokens. Chonk owners can collect, trade, equip, unequip and mint new Traits.
